data.description: Welcome to 1912 Snyder Ave, a delightful residence in the picturesque Alpine Acres neighborhood of Colorado Springs. This charming home seamlessly blends modern comforts with classic charm, creating an inviting atmosphere for you and your loved ones. Step inside to find spacious interiors bathed in natural light, connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen'an ideal space for entertaining guests and spending quality time with family.    With five comfortable bedrooms, including a tranquil owner's suite with an ensuite bathroom, this home provides cozy retreats after a long day. Venture outside to your private outdoor paradise'an ideal spot for summer barbecues and relaxation under the vast Colorado sky.    The basement unfolds into a family room,  ideal for movie nights and unwinding. Two additional bedrooms and a third bathroom enhance the functionality of this level, making it ideal for larger families or hosting guests overnight. The basement also offers an oversized laundry and storage space, providing endless possibilities for organization and creativity.    Conveniently located in the heart of the Alpine Acres neighborhood, this property offers easy access to local schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining establishments. Commuting is effortless, with major highways and public transportation options nearby. Meticulously maintained, this home promises a turnkey experience for its new owners. Don't miss the opportunity to embrace the comfort, convenience, and natural beauty of Colorado Springs. Schedule a showing today and step into your dream home. 2023-11-27
